org.forgerock.openidm.sync.impl

Class SynchronizationService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openidm.sync.impl.SynchronizationService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.forgerock.json.resource.SingletonResourceProvider, org.forgerock.openidm.quartz.impl.ScheduledService, Mappings

    @Properties(value={@Property(name="service.description",value="OpenIDM object synchronization service"),@Property(name="service.vendor",value="ForgeRock AS"),@Property(name="openidm.router.prefix",value="/sync/*")})
@Service
public class SynchronizationService
extends Object
implements org.forgerock.json.resource.SingletonResourceProvider, Mappings, org.forgerock.openidm.quartz.impl.ScheduledService
    The resource provider for requests on /sync. Describes the synchronization mappings and dispatches actions to synchronize between source and targets listed in the synchronization mappings described by the sync.json configuration file. Also supports invocation as a ScheduledService.
